tests.title: Proquest

err.message:
CypressError: Timed out retrying: cy.type() failed because this element:

<input type="text" name="searchKeyword" placeholder="Search Products & Services" aria-label="Search box to search entire site" data-provide="typeahead" class="form-control  input-sm  typeahead  tt-query" style="border: none; position: relative; vertical-align: top; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block;" autocomplete="off" spellcheck="false" dir="auto">

is being covered by another element:

<iframe src="https://consent-pref.trustarc.com/?type=proquest&site=proquest.com&action=notice&country=gb&locale=en&behavior=expressed&layout=default_eu&irm=false&from=https://consent.trustarc.com/" id="pop-frame0622426287861362" title="TrustArc Cookie Consent Manager" tabindex="1" scrolling="no" style="border: 0px; border-radius: 2px; overflow: hidden; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: block; position: absolute; top: 0px; left: 0px; width: 100%; height: 282px;"></iframe>

Fix this problem, or use {force: true} to disable error checking.

https://on.cypress.io/element-cannot-be-interacted-with
